OL,6,FFormer and England star Danny Murphy
OL,7,Fhas revealed he suffered a "world of
OL,8,Fpain" after developing a cocaine
OL,9,Faddiction following his retirement
OL,10,Ffrom football.
OL,12,FMurphy, 47, who also played for ,
OL,13,FCharlton, Tottenham, Fulham and , has
OL,14,Fadmitted that the Class A drug "grabs
OL,15,Fhold of you."
OL,17,FSince ending his playing career in
OL,18,F2013, he has worked as a pundit, but
OL,19,Fsaid: "When you don't have football,
OL,20,Fproblems become huge."
