OL,6,FDanny, who is originally from ,
OL,7,Fattended therapy sessions and support
OL,8,Fgroups which he says helped in his
OL,9,Frecovery.
OL,11,F"You lose that shame and guilt when
OL,12,Fyou're around people who've gone
OL,13,Fthrough it too because you start
OL,14,Fthinking 'am I the only one who is
OL,15,Fweak?'"
